## 2. Vercel (vercel.com)

Vercel is the benchmark for modular, "Bento Box" design. They manage an incredibly complex suite of products by keeping everything tightly boxed with minimal sub-pixel borders.

### Global Navigation Hierarchy
`Products` • `Resources` • `Solutions` • `Enterprise` • [Pricing](file:///c:/Users/abe/OneDrive/NexaOS/src/pages/Pricing.tsx#6-96) • `Log In` • `Ask AI` • **[ Sign Up ]**

### Exact Homepage Section Order
1. **Dynamic Hero:** "Build and deploy on the AI Cloud." (Primary CTA: "Start Deploying", Secondary: "Get a Demo").
2. **Interactive Selection Grid:** A tabbed interface allowing users to select their workflow ("Deploy AI Apps in seconds").
3. **Product Bento Grid:** A massive, multi-tiered grid highlighting their core modules (Agents, Web Apps, Commerce).
4. **Technical Deep Dive:** "Framework-defined infrastructure."
5. **Enterprise Proof:** Blocks dedicated to Security, Scale, and Performance.
6. **Global Network Map:** Visualizing their edge nodes.
7. **Customer Testimonials:** Large-scale quotes.
8. **Template Grid & Final CTA.**

